_sText:
Fun little map I made in a few days, color themed setting in space for a change. :^) Avoided flat gameplay as much as I could and went for a different style this time around. 

Nofail map, No checkpoints. Good run 1:07~  Also has a short bonus which is essentially just bhop_docks without the godawful ending.

Hope y'all enjoy. Big thanks to dream for testing for me, and providing the video. Feel free to sub to him for future impressive uploads.
